caption.p: Power spectral analysis of human brainwaves characterized by frequencies consisting of delta, theta, alpha, and beta wave powers in control, 1:1000 dilution, 1:400 dilution, 1:100 dilution, and undiluted garlic oil groups. Not significant (ns), *, **, *** and **** represent no statistical differences, p < 0.05, and p < 0.01, p < 0.001, and p < 0.0001, respectively.
